						               													<description>Pop the top to &amp;ldquo;roll&amp;rdquo; the dice! Race to collect and match the cake topping card to build your cupcake!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Assemble your cupcake in order by colour, case, cake, icing and cherry. The case colour determines the cupcake you make. Keep an eye out for your colour! If you roll the &amp;lsquo;swap&amp;rsquo; arrows, you can swap cakes with the opponent of your choice.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If you roll the Cake Monster&amp;rsquo;s mouth your cake is guzzled and its back to the start! The player who creates the perfect cupcake first wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash; description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On a player's turn they roll the dice which show a shape and a color of the part of the cake. Immediately each player has to grab the corresponding tile. The colors of the tiles are hidden because the tiles lay face down, so at first no one knows which is correct. But during the game players can memorize which tiles lay where. The dice also show two special effect, one of each orders the active player to return particular piece, while another allow players to steal from others. The first player to collect 3 different pieces of a cupcake wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash; user summary&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
